{
  "stem": "9601.2",
  "chunk_idx": 8,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "At the same time-- a little bit something during hat same time-- they begin to arrest people in the village.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "You know, this-- the arrests were usually done by the Polish government during the night.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "When you came in the morning, you heard, oh, this man was taken away.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And this man, the police took away.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And this one took away, and they found a spy over there in the barn.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "It wasn't actually a spy, he was an activist.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "But he had to be underground, so he was in the barn.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And they arrested a lot of young people-- young men.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "But later on, I figured out this was in the summer.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "The arrests were done early in the summer-- so, like, June.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "But I figured out later on after the War ended.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "You know, you just think.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "You grow up.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "You begin to understand things.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "Those were the people-- excuse me-- that were attending college-- gymnasiums.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "That's why all the political indoctrination, political education, political activism was being conducted.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "But when they came home for the summer, they were easy picking.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "So that's why they used to be arrested.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "I found out later.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "But up till then, I didn't know, you know, there was all this stuff going on.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "Later, when the Soviets took over-- when the Soviets took over Poland in 1939, all of these young people were let out of the jails.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "Political prisoners were all liberated by the Soviets.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "Ah!",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "It was nice.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "Everybody was happy.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "Our young men are back.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "But I want to tell you.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "None of the Jewish people were ever arrested for political activism, because they did not participate.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They knew that you've got to keep your nose clean and stay away from politics.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I think they did, because never happened.",
      "word_count": 7
    }
  ],
